query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN detailedDescription IS NOT NULL AND detailedDescription != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_desc,
  SUM(CASE WHEN particleSize IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_particle,
  SUM(CASE WHEN poreSize IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_pore,
  SUM(CASE WHEN specifications IS NOT NULL AND specifications != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_specs
FROM products
